「社区精华」PUBG 鼠标DPI浅析 （转载并翻译）
这篇文章是在国外网站看到的对于PUBG游戏DPI设置的一些简单分析，觉得挺有用的，就自行翻译搬运给大家。之所以翻译的目的是因为我发现有很多玩家对于外设的理解仍处于懵懂状态甚至无知。谨以贡献知识的卑微态度奉献给大家，希望大家都能有所得，有所体会，有所想，有所成。- GHS_gad正文如下：What Mouse DPI Do I ReallyNeed for FPS Gaming? 我到底需要多少的鼠标DPI来玩FPS游戏？There are 2 key points for play PUBG, the game mouse and game earphone should be veryimportant! A good game mouse should consider a lot, spends a big amount ofmoney for a performance mouse is not enough. So how should we choose a good game mouse?对于玩PUBG的玩家来说，有两样东西至关重要，那就是游戏鼠标和游戏耳机。一个好的游戏鼠标应当设计周全，只是花很多钱去买一个贵的鼠标的考量是不够的。那么我们应该如何挑选一个合适的好用的游戏鼠标呢？What mouseDPI do I really need for FPS gaming? Here are some advice about how to chooseand setting’s experience for you!我到底应该用多少DPI去玩FPS游戏呢？以下就是关于如何挑选和设置游戏鼠标的一些建议。1. Mouse acceleration1. 鼠标加速First, makesure that you have turn off the game mouse acceleration when you are playingFPS. What is mouse acceleration? The cursor moves the same distance across thescreen at different speeds when the mouse moves the same distance across themat. This seriously affects the targeting of the game .首先，请确保在你玩FPS游戏的时候鼠标加速功能是关闭的。什么是鼠标加速？当你的鼠标在鼠标垫上移动相同距离时，屏幕上的指针以不同速度移动了相对应的同等距离就是鼠标加速。这会严重影响游戏内的瞄准定位。Firstly, let’s turn on the system SETTINGS> DEVICE > MOUSE > OTHER MOUSE > POINTER >ENHANCE POINTER PRECISION, removed the ✅ here. Thetop selection moves at a default speed of 6/11, do not change it. This settingcan avoid most of the mouse acceleration, but it also can not 1:1 reduction themouse movement, like the popular hardcore FPS game CSGO.There is an option in the mouse SETTINGS called the original data input in thegame, turn this option on can totally avoid the speed of the mouse from effectof the WINDOWS system, directly read movement trajectory from it, there is nosuch settings options on PUBG.第一步，让我们打开控制面板》设备》鼠标》高级设置》指针选项，找到提高鼠标精准度，将勾选去掉。第二步，将鼠标的系统灵敏度设置在第6格，系统默认既如此，不要改动。当然，如果你的鼠标驱动软件可以单独设置鼠标加速，那么在硬核FPS游戏CSGO中你就可以通过设置中的启动鼠标输入数据来规避windows系统的鼠标设置。可惜的是PUBG这款游戏没有类似功能。 2. Without DPI sensitivity the game are meaningless 2. 没有了DPI灵敏度，射击游戏将毫无意义Most playerswill focus on the value of their basic sensitivity, shoulder shot and fourtimes eight times rate of the game, but seldomly mention the DPI value, it’sactually meaningless. When the mouse in different DPI, the speed won’t be thesame during the same sensitivity in the game.大多数玩家非常注重游戏中的常规灵敏度，肩射灵敏度，4倍/8倍灵敏度，却很少注意到鼠标DPI的配值，这没有任何意义。因为当鼠标处在不同DPI的时候，游戏内准星移动的速度将会随着不同DPI有着不同的结果，尽管你设置同样的灵敏度（gad:这不是废话么，这段不翻译也成）DPI is shortfrom Dots Per Inch, means the pixel points value about the mouse move one Inch cursorof the mouse mat on the screen, the more pixels Per Inch the higher the DPI,and the speed of mouse will be much faster, 1080 p screen resolution ratebetween 1600 DPI to 2000 DPI can reach most people’s need currently, the higherDPI of the engine the more stability at low DPI.(mainstream engine model:PMW3310 PMW3360 PMW3366 PMW3389)DPI是每英寸上的点数的缩写，意即鼠标在鼠标垫上移动一英寸指针在显示器上走过的像素点数。走过的点数越多，DPI对应的就越高，也意味着鼠标的移动速度越快。现如今，1600DPI-2000DPI能满足大多数使用1080P的显示器的人们。当你的鼠标传感器能驾驭越高的DPI，那么它就能在低DPI时体现更稳定的性能。（主流传感器：PMW 3310, 3360, 3366 3389）(gad添一句：ec-a系列是3310， ec-b系列是3360，G403是3366，蝰蛇是3389)A lot of FPSprofessional player prefer to choose 400 DPI and the sensitivity is low in thegame. To those lower DPI sensitivity game, when using the mouse on the mousemat to move larger distance, we should move fewer pixels on the screen. It willbe better for player to do the target control and trimming more easy in thegame. Good for muscle memory formation after a long training, more accuratepositioning when the player instantly pull a gun on the game. There are onething that need to be mention about is that many manufacturers will have aspecial adjustment or customization service about the engine, different brand’sgame mouse with the same DPI speed will also have a slight difference, whichrequires you to experience, we recommended you to choose the original phase ofthe PMW3310 engine mouse, which will be more stable.绝大多数FPS职业玩家倾向于使用400 DPI搭配游戏内低灵敏度，对于低DPI灵敏度而言，由于在鼠标垫上移动大距离时，显示器上的像素位移相对较少，这会给玩家带来很大的好处，尤其是在瞄准目标和修正目标时将更加轻松。（gad:这个非常重要，简单说就是低DPI的容错率更高）进而更容易在长时间训练下养成肌肉记忆，并且能帮助玩家在对枪的第一时间更精准的预瞄。这里需要点一下很多鼠标厂商会对游戏传感器进行一些改进和改良，不同品牌的游戏鼠标在相同DPI的情况下，鼠标速度可能略有不同，这需要你花时间去体会，这里我推荐始用PMW3310初代的传感器，因为其相对稳定（gad：用过ec2-a, ec2-b， G403,狗屁王,对于PUBG来说，EC2-A的3310传感器手感最差，因为自带线性修正功能，会让鼠标反应稍微的慢一点点，但是说它稳定倒是没错）3. Mouse refresh rate鼠标刷新率Generallyspeaking, mouse refresh rate is the evaluation speed of mouse and computer dataexchange. For example, the mouse of our early PS2 interface can only reach 125HZ, which need to be improved by software overfrequency. 125 HZ means refreshrate in every 0.008 seconds, 1000 HZ means refresh rate in every 0.001 seconds,the higher the mouse per second the more data collected, which is one of themouse performance indicators. Most professional players choose the refresh rateon 500 HZ or 10000 HZ, this can effectively guarantee the stability of themouse, the higher frequency the higher CPU occupancy rate.通俗来讲，鼠标刷新率就是鼠标和计算机之间对数据的回馈速率。比如，早期PS2界面的鼠标只能达到125赫兹，需要超频才能得到提升。125赫兹意味着回馈率是每0.008秒鼠标和计算机交换一次数据，而1000赫兹的回馈率是0.001秒，刷新率越高，那么鼠标每秒采集到的数据就越多，这也是鼠标性能的指标之一。大多数职业玩家的鼠标刷新率会设置在500赫兹-1000赫兹，这会非常有效的保证鼠标的操作稳定性，但是越高的刷新率会造成CPU更高的占有率。（gad:鼠标这点刷新率根本对CPU造成不了什么大消耗，建议1000赫兹）4.Game sensitivity游戏灵敏度Let’s talk about the sensitivity on the PUBG. Thesensitivity is more thinner in this game compare to other FPS game, thesensitivity of different situation can be set up separately. We can notcalculate a player’s accurately eDPI value (mouse DPI multiplied to sensitivityof the game) on the CSGO project. It’s not smart to copy the mouse settingsfrom those professional players. But we still can learn from them, many PUBGplayers have seen “North American’s first breakthrough hand” shroud’s game playcollection, the marksmanship from him is remarkable from the game and letpeople doubt that they are playing the same game.现在让我们来谈一谈PUBG的游戏灵敏度。PUBG的游戏灵敏度相较于其他FPS游戏来说更加细致，很多不同情况下的灵敏度可以分开设置。我们不能计算一个玩家精确的eDPI数值（eDPI是鼠标的DPI乘以游戏内灵敏度的数值。Gad注：比如CSGO：400DPI，1.85的游戏灵敏度就是740的eDPI）。简单的从职业选手那里抄鼠标配置其实不要是很科学的做法。(gad:毕竟需要平衡自己习惯的和将要适应的，最好慢慢缓冲。) 但是我们仍可以从职业玩家的设置中学到一些东西，比如北美第一突破手shroud的游戏设置非常受欢迎，因为其令人难忘的精彩操作使人不禁怀疑大家是否玩的是同一款游戏。That’s all for today. Hope every player can find theirown mouse sensitivity through more actual combat on the game, defeat the enemywith one shoot ! WINNER WINNER , CHICKEN DINNER!这就是今天我要说的全部。希望每个玩家都可以找到属于自己的鼠标灵敏度，横扫战场，一击致命。大吉大利，今晚吃鸡！Reference:Ragnok Mousegun原文链接：https://www.ragnok.net/news/gaming-mouse-setup-guide/?v=6cc98ba2045f本文来源：小黑盒由小黑盒 gad 翻译整理
